description:
Welcome back to TACTICAL AWARENESS - a Canadian Podcast about Corvus Belli’s landmark Sci-Fi Wargame; Infinity N5. Come along with our hosts Ash, Owen and Dan for a whole new ITS Edition of Infinity! 

We're back with Zeroes & Heroes; our new Faction review segment where Owen, Dan and Ash will each build their own N5 take on a faction! We're back with the start of a new series as we kick into the JSA with OBAN!
